 rifl exercis . After tea went down town met Taylor with whom had a drink . Went on Road picquet at 7.30 p.m. went off 9.45 p.m. Tuesday , 5/6/17 Threw more live bomb in morn drill with box respir . Receiv letter from Guild Uncle Fred . Evene took stroll down the town . Wednesday , 6/6/17 Fine sunshin . Wrote home . After tea went down town . Thursday , 7/6/17 Rather warm today . In morn went through real gas . One chap out . After tea went down town . Wrote letter to Guild . Friday , 8/6/17 Went rout march for the day to Corf Castl back by differ road , total 10 mile . Had dinner near the Castl had 1 hour off to see it the town . Extra good meal today . After tea went to town read paper . Saturday , 9/6/17 Fair warm . Feet slight sore after march . When came back from bull-r at 12.30 , Reg was wait for me , had been wait hour . Stop about hr . then he motor to Bournemouth . Sunday , 10/6/17 Warm day ? got up 7 a.m. In morn took stroll up valley gather nice wild flower .
